	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I thought it might be a good idea to dis-assemble a rom for the purpose of studying it's code, particularly it's code as it applies to the sound registers. 
<br />
<br />Could anyone recommend a good (relatively simple) rom for this?
<br />
<br />Also, what could I use the dis-assemble?
<br />
<br />Thanks again,
<br />T

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


